How to start application with docker
    Start docker
    Run in PowerShell
        - cd (path of file\DevOps)
        - pip install requirements.txt
        - docker build -t flask-app .
        - docker run -d -p 5000:5000 flask-app || docker run -it flask-app

    in browser
        - localhost:5000/
        - localhost:5000/hello/"name" -> additional function

Additional PowerShell commands
    - docker ps -> shows running containers
    - docker ps -a -> shows all containers
    - docker stop <id> -> zatrzymuje kontener